Relative validity of a mobile AI-technology assisted dietary assessment in adolescent females in Vietnam.
AI assisted dietary assessment and 24HR accurately estimate nutrient intake in adolescent females when compared to WR. Errors could be reduced with further improvements of AI-assisted food recognition and portion estimation.
